/**
 * skymesh-bridge tests.
 *
 * Run via the gnosis test runner:  ./bin/monster test rtlsdr-mock-sim/skymesh-bridge.test.ts
 * (NOT raw vitest -- the gnosis harness wraps it.)
 *
 * Each integration test stands up:
 *   - a mock LOCAL monitor (node:http) on loopback exposing /monitor/scenes,
 *     /monitor/status, /monitor/stream (SSE) and POST /monitor/control, and
 *   - a mock RELAY (ws WebSocketServer) on loopback at /monitor/bridge,
 * then drives a real SkymeshBridge against them and asserts the FIXED uplink
 * protocol (frame/status/scenes UP, control DOWN -> control-result UP) and the
 * reconnect/backoff behaviour.
 */
